- (WNWordObject *) wordObjectByAppendingElementsFromWord: (WNWordObject *)  other

Return a new Word that is a copy of the receiving word, with all elements contained in otherWord appended or appropriately coalesced.

This may be used to combine multiple word records for the same word, fetched from different sources, into a common word record.

Parameters:
otherAn existing word record.

A block that accepts two arrays, filters values from the second arrays that occur in the first array, and then appends the second array to the first.

The block correctly handles the case where either value is nil.
